title: Brigata "Salerno" - 89th Reggimento Fanteria
text:
World War Reenacting | 89th Reggimento Fanteria
top of pageThis site was designed with the .com website builder. Create your website today.Start NowBrigata "Salerno"
89/90thReggimento
Avanti Savoia!HOMETHE UNITHISTORYARTICLESCONTACTMoreUse tab to navigate through the menu items.We are a living history and reenactment organization located on the East Coast that is committed to representing the Royal Italian Army in the First World War. Our goal is to accurately portray the typical Italian regiment; including infantry and Arditi. We seek to accurately recreate the appearance, duties, and life of the front for the Royal Italian army.
​
Our organization specifically reenacts the Salerno Brigade of the 89/90th Regiment of infantry, if you are wanting to learn more we have a page depicting the whole history of the unit and the Italian army during the war. We reenact both campaigns of the Italian army from the stationing of the Western Front to the Italian front.
If you want to join the ranks of our reenactment community, go to our contact page and our recruitment officer will place you in the unit. Avanti Savoia!HOMETHE UNITHISTORYARTICLESCONTACTMoreUse tab to navigate through the menu items.bottom of page
